{"tid":2406140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民間「煙花滙」炮仗聲四起","createTime":"2021-02-13T03:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T03:55:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f21613b6500c93d80b1eaa2b73e0b93041d1e5","tid":2406140,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T03:14:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210213/KY643FPUNJD7BBXQXRGQPP3LGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210213%2FKY643FPUNJD7BBXQXRGQPP3LGU%2F&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQzyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=cdd6de61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210213%2FKY643FPUNJD7BBXQXRGQPP3LGU%2F&h=401e7e40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210213/KY643FPUNJD7BBXQXRGQPP3LGU/</a><br />\n<br />\n民間「煙花滙」炮仗聲四起<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/c_P7NRTejLPv15kS5ah_QrQgYxI=/1565x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ODQBSUEHFNCCRBJIQ3VVXMJ2VI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fc_P7NRTejLPv15kS5ah_QrQgYxI%3D%2F1565x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FODQBSUEHFNCCRBJIQ3VVXMJ2VI.jpg&h=5bdcfb8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大年初一凌晨有人在啟德港鐵站外放煙花。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】受疫情影響，官方農曆新年。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：50辣車放煙花狂飆 當警無到<br />\n<br />\n民間「煙花騷」此起彼落，荃灣中心連接1座往2座的天橋昨晚10時許有人燃點煙花，持續數分鐘，煙花射上十多層樓高，居民鬧爆，網傳警方帶走兩人。前晚11時左右，沙田禾寮坑、黃泥頭及九肚村；以至午夜後馬鞍山亞公角街、元朗屏山；甚至啟德港鐵站外、秀茂坪寶達邨、黃大仙聯合道及油麻地果欄鬧市，均出現「賀歲煙花」。<br />\n<br />\n有居民拍攝到油麻地果欄附近燃燒煙花，夜空萬紫千紅，持續近一分鐘，煙花射上十多層樓高，在民居附近爆破，有汽車駛經旁邊西九龍走廊時亦減速慢駛。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：人潮湧西貢 露營友與牛過年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n區議員轟危及果欄附近居民<br />\n<br />\n油麻地天主教小學對開澄平街，地面遺有兩個已爆裂的紙箱及碎屑；該處相隔僅一條渡船街的對面，便是新油麻地警署。「煙花騷」期間，警方表示接獲多宗報案，但均沒有發現。鬧市煙花燃爆，油尖旺區議員胡穗珊事後在fb出帖，批評鬧市放煙花很危險，又指旁邊果欄附近存有很多易燃紙箱，「怎可以貪一時的高興為居民帶來風險！」<br />\n<br />\n香港法例禁止燃放炮仗，然而，新。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3LtlN5cZipWu8Tbmg41B7Mofzr0=/1311x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5BWZLOQYSRASTO642R7UUVFVMI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3LtlN5cZipWu8Tbmg41B7Mofzr0%3D%2F1311x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5BWZLOQYSRASTO642R7UUVFVMI.jpg&h=aa4c6e29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■新界村民昨早按傳統燃燒炮仗，迎接新歲。"},{"pid":"156e9dd6ed817a582f8b371d3f0cac21b5d73a26","tid":2406140,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T03:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e210d1d5dba40ac93dc6de887e793980930838c7","tid":2406140,"uid":19640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T03:16:31.000Z","msg":"柒婆搞到成個政府執法都無信服力，係人都唔撚驚犯法，反正屋企有石油氣BB彈都已經犯國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3989468ca31a196f3b6358b1bada0ef4203dc9c","tid":2406140,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T03:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd50cc100d8a08a77848bdde1226ef66b0a56177","tid":2406140,"uid":276273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T03:19:49.000Z","msg":"鄉黑就鄉黑，講乜撚野民間，<br />\n個班只係鄉黑嚟"},{"pid":"e498e07618f9bb57e65fc4f2b5f602607b1b2485","tid":2406140,"uid":274772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7f21613b6500c93d80b1eaa2b73e0b93041d1e5","tid":2406140,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T03:14:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210213/KY643FPUNJD7BBXQXRGQPP3LGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.a